  "remarks": "Member of the Federation Council from Omsk region. Senator and Deputy Chair of the Federation Council Committee on Constitutional Legislation and State Building since September 2015.  Former Head of the Family Affairs Committee in the State Duma.  Originator and co-sponsor of legislative proposals in Russia that allow regions of other countries to join Russia without their central authorities’ agreement; Listing: Listed on 19 Jun. 2014 (relisted on 16 Jun. 2017 and 10 June 2023)",
